    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's time to feel the rhythm through notes and hit them with rhythm!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LEZ</strong> is a rhythm game in the style of osu!mania with 6 keys. It's an indie game made by only one person in July 2020 with the goal to make a creative rhythm game with an unique design. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1857370/extras/6116c0f1f3c56fa771da6400c193d2f8.avif?t=1764289657\" width=600 height=174 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A streamer mode for content creators (and also youtubers), we really care about them :D </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of songs by professional and well know artists. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Integration with Logitech G Hub to feel the music through the RGB </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you feel the beatmaps very hard or very easy? There's mods that you can use to increase/decrease the difficulty</p></li></ul>",
